data.title: Quarles: Attorneys, Lawyers, Law Firm
data.meta_description: Quarles is a multidisciplinary Am Law 200 firm with approximately 520 attorneys practicing at the top of the profession in Chicago, Denver, Indianapolis, Madison, Milwaukee, Minneapolis, Naples, Phoenix, San Diego, Tampa, Tucson and Washington, D.C.
